videos.headline: Scott fumbles at goal line
videos.description: LJ Scott fumbles at the goal line and Bowling Green returns it 30 yards.

videos.headline: Michigan State scores 1st TD of season
videos.description: Madre London rushes for a 7-yard touchdown in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Lewerke scrambles for a Michigan State first  down
videos.description: Brian Lewerke avoids being sacked and runs for a 12-yard gain.

videos.headline: Bowling Green's Garth ejected for targeting
videos.description: Fred Garth is issued a personal foul for targeting against Michigan State .

videos.headline: Lewerke to Davis strikes again for TD
videos.description: Felton Davis catches his second touchdown to extend Michigan State's lead.

videos.headline: Lewerke fires 3rd TD pass of the game
videos.description: Brian Lewerke finds Matt Sokol for a 13-yard touchdown in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Bowling Green scopes up fumble for a TD.
videos.description: LJ. Scott fumbles the ball and Cameron Jefferies picks it up for a 46-yard touchdown.
